title: Is 5 AD the new Meta, or are the players in Bronze high on something?
body: Just finished a game that had 5 AD on the enemy team and no tank, needless to say, we smashed them.

replies.body: they're bronze, they can't get high

Hey,
Congrats on winning your game! 5 ad is not the new meta, but some people in Bronze pay no regard to team comps. That is most likely the case in your experience as they just wanted to play Champs they liked.

Yours sincerely, 
Talwyn
But there were a few in game stating that to be true, 5 AD as the new meta, but yeh, bronze is bronze.
